            <h2 class="mb-4">About Confessions</h2>

            <p>Welcome to Confessions, a safe space where you can share your thoughts, secrets, and experiences anonymously. Our platform was created with a simple yet powerful mission: to provide a judgment-free environment where people can express themselves honestly and find connection through shared experiences.</p>

            <p>Whether it's a lighthearted admission about never watching a popular show, a workplace confession about pretending to understand the latest tech buzzwords, or a more serious reflection on life's challenges, your voice matters here. Every confession contributes to a tapestry of human experiences that reminds us we're not alone in our thoughts and feelings.</p>

            <p>How it works:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Share your confession anonymously - no account needed</li>
                <li>Connect with others through likes and comments</li>
                <li>Choose a nickname when commenting to maintain anonymity</li>
                <li>Use simple formatting to express yourself (bold, italic, underline, strikethrough)</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Our community guidelines are simple: be respectful, be honest, and remember that behind every confession and comment is a real person. While you can't edit or delete your own confessions (to maintain the integrity of conversations), our administrators ensure the space remains safe and supportive for everyone.</p>

            <p>Ready to unburden yourself or connect with others' experiences? Join our community of truth-tellers and start sharing today.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>